Revision history for Domain-Sift

0.2.0   2025/12/13
        Added extract_domains() and contains_domains() for multi-domain extraction.
        CLI now extracts all domains per line instead of just the first.
        Added RFC 8552 support for underscore-prefixed service records
        (_dmarc, _spf, _443._tcp, etc.).
        Externalized TLD list to tlds.txt with automated weekly sync via PR.
        Performance improvements: possessive quantifiers, cached patterns,
        index() fast paths.

0.1.2   2023/09/04
        Cleaned up README and added more information.
        Updated TLD list in Domain::Sift::Match.
0.1.1   2023/08/26
        Added more tests.
        Whitespace and style fixes.
0.1.0   2023/07/25
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.
